<!--
Dark color theme for the application. Every component inside the
application has an Appearance attribute. The "applyTo" attribute
of the tags specify the component inside the application that should
implement the values specified in that "Appearance" tag.
Editor Appearances are also applied to inspectors as they basically
look the same.
-->
